{"tid":2077292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際商會警告：全盤皆落索","createTime":"2020-06-24T07:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T07:34:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b3f51abc00095aa9bf23d624dc262f913f02b0","tid":2077292,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/3WYVFWRXTIOYF5UU67M7WCMCLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F3WYVFWRXTIOYF5UU67M7WCMCLU%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPrJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=f16be2e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2F3WYVFWRXTIOYF5UU67M7WCMCLU%2F&h=aca98ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/3WYVFWRXTIOYF5UU67M7WCMCLU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國際商會警告：全盤皆落索<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4PVA5KR4XMHGGBLB6CTRPNPDLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4PVA5KR4XMHGGBLB6CTRPNPDLA.jpg&h=cc238f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國際商會香港區會周一發表意見書，批評中共訂立港區國安法，將令香港失去自由、法治的保護傘。該會主席、前法律援助局主席李澤培（圖）回覆本報查詢時說，企業應自行決定觀望、部署短期或長期決定，但相信商界會加緊考慮撤資等長期部署的準備。<br />\n<br />\n對於終審法院前首席法官李國能認為，行政長官不應該挑選法官審理國安法案件，若有案件移送內地受審，會損害司法獨立，李澤培表示尊重，並稱「所謂一子錯，全（滿）盤皆落索」。<br />\n<br />\n李澤培表示，。。。、短期部署或長期決定，「決定不一」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n營商警覺再提高<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刑事案法官絕非特首指派<br />\n<br />\n李國能昨日在《明報》撰文，認為行政長官不應該挑選法官審理國安法案件，李澤培對此表示：「我們尊重李國能前首席法官的意見。所謂一子錯，全盤皆落索」。<br />\n<br />\n出身商界的李澤培曾出任多項公職，包括法律援助局主席、社會服務聯會主席、義務工作發展局主席等。<br />\n<br />\n李在任國際商會香港區會主席其間，。。。，現任副主席則是香港民主促進會成員高德禮（George Cautherley）。"},{"pid":"78dc85dabd5d17c29ded45f48015c20b2d16d78d","tid":2077292,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"第一個<br />\n捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}